OL,3,CCouncil to pay compensation after
OL,4,Csudden closure of dementia care home
OL,6,FHazel Garth Care Home in Knottingley,
OL,7,Fwas closed by Wakefield Council in May
OL,8,F2024, leaving six families with just a
OL,9,Fday to prepare their elderly relatives
OL,10,Ffor eviction.
OL,12,FMost were picked up in taxis the
OL,13,Ffollowing day and moved into
OL,14,Falternative accommodation.
OL,16,FWakefield council said the sudden
OL,17,Fclosure was due to the home being
OL,18,Fshort-staffed and the building needed
OL,19,Frepairs.
OL,21,FWhat did the independent review find?
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
