OL,3,CCouncil to pay compensation after
OL,4,Csudden closure of dementia care home
OL,6,FGillian Marshall, the council's chief
OL,7,Flegal officer, said: "The compensation
OL,8,Fwas a recommendation from the
OL,9,Findependent review.
OL,11,F"And we fully agree that it was right
OL,12,Fand proper for the council to make an
OL,13,Fappropriate payment of compensation.
OL,15,F"This has now been agreed and, out of
OL,16,Frespect to the families involved, we
OL,17,Fwon't be releasing any further
OL,18,Fdetails."
